file.name: valid-openapi.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.1.0
servers:
  - url: http://example.xyz
info:
  description: Example description
  version: '1.0'
  title: Example title
  license:
    name: MIT
    url: 'https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT'
paths:
  /pet/findByStatus:
    get:
      summary: needExist
      operationId: findByStatus
      responses:
        '200':
          description: example description
        '400':
          description: some desc
